{"title":"【log】记录一次nodejs安装依赖的报错","date":"2021-01-25T04:52:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 25, 2021","L":"01/25/2021","MM-DD":"01-25"},"link":"2021/01/25/2021-01-25-01","comments":true,"tags":["nodejs"],"updated":"2021-01-25T04:53:50.857Z","content":"<p>安装依赖的时候，显示node的权限不够，错误如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh: 1: node: Permission denied</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>解决办法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config set user 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config set unsafe-perm true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","next":{"title":"【golang】记录一次go mod在jetbrain 设定的问题","link":"2021/01/15/2021-01-15-01"},"plink":"https://terence.segofun.com/2021/01/25/2021-01-25-01/"}